headline: Excellent Execution Drove IDEXX Laboratories (IDXX) Shares Amid Macro Challenges

headline: Integra LifeSciences (IART) Beats Q2 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Integra (IART) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +4.65% and +5.05%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
